\n\n4. **结论**：\n   - Redis 的性能问题是根本原因，而 `cartservice` 的进程异常是 Redis 延迟的连锁反应。需要优先排查 Redis 的性能瓶颈。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "cartservice Pods (cartservice-0, cartservice-1, cartservice-2) are the root cause due to pod_processes abnormal increase from 1.0 to 13.0 and pod_cpu_usage surge", "current_task_instruction": "当前处于【分析阶段】。\n以下是你可以访问的全量上下文信息，包含了用户输入、当前假设、以及其他所有智能体的历史发现：\n================================\nUUID: 88f808ff-426\n\nUser Query: Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-21T11:10:22Z and 2025-06-21T11:22:22Z and provide the root cause.\n\n\n[RAW DATA CONTEXT]\n\n--- Raw Log Data ---\n{'status': 'success', 'message': '成功加载日志数据。UUID: 88f808ff-426，共 2 条错误日志', 'filtered_logs': 'node_name,service_name,pod_name,message,occurrence_count\\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,\"2025-06-21 11:11:31,827 main WARN Could not create ContextDataInjector for \\'io.opencensus.contrib.logcorrelation.log4j2.OpenCensusTraceContextDataInjector\\', using default org.apache.logging.log4j.core.impl.ThreadContextDataInjector$ForCopyOnWriteThreadContextMap: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: io.opencensus.contrib.logcorrelation.log4j2.OpenCensusTraceContextDataInjector\",出现次数:1\\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,\"2025-06-21 11:11:40,024 main WARN Could not create ContextDataInjector for \\'io.opencensus.contrib.logcorrelation.log4j2.OpenCensusTraceContextDataInjector\\', using default org.apache.logging.log4j.core.impl.ThreadContextDataInjector$ForCopyOnWriteThreadContextMap: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: io.opencensus.contrib.logcorrelation.log4j2.OpenCensusTraceContextDataInjector\",出现次数:1\\n', 'unique_entities': {'pod_name': ['adservice-1'], 'service_name': ['adservice'], 'node_name': ['aiops-k8s-07']}, 'matched_anomaly': 'Please analyze the abnormal event betwe